Bush

+--
Utilities for Minecraft Internet scanning project.
+--

utils/check/check.go
--------------------
Check Minecraft servers from STDIN

utils/generate/generate.go
--------------------------
Generate host:port from cidr/file and ports range

utils/randomize/randomize.go
----------------------------
Shuffle STDIN
Used to prevent VPS providers to find out you are scanning their network and ban you.

utils/database
--------------
Used to store scanned hosts in a MongoDB database.

build.sh
--------
Build the file above to out/

sample command
--------------
./generate -cidr 51.79.0.0/16 -ports 25565,25566 | ./randomize | ./check -threads 100 | tee output.json | jq -c
